@host=http://localhost:8080
@userId=1
@packageId=2
@outTradeNo=202405041234567890

### ======== 钱包管理接口 ========

### 获取用户钱包信息
GET {{host}}/userplat/wallet/info?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 获取余额流水记录
GET {{host}}/userplat/wallet/flow/list?userId={{userId}}&pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 创建充值订单
POST {{host}}/userplat/wallet/recharge?userId={{userId}}&packageId={{packageId}}&payChannel=WXPAY&tradeType=JSAPI
Content-Type: application/json

### ======== 充值套餐接口 ========

### 获取充值套餐列表
GET {{host}}/userplat/recharge/package/list
Content-Type: application/json

### 获取充值套餐列表（后台管理）
GET {{host}}/userplat/recharge/package/list/admin?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&enableState=1
Content-Type: application/json

### 获取充值套餐详情
GET {{host}}/userplat/recharge/package/detail?packageId={{packageId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 新增充值套餐
POST {{host}}/userplat/recharge/package
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "packageName": "测试套餐",
  "rechargeMoney": 88.00,
  "giftMoney": 8.80,
  "enableState": 1
}

### 修改充值套餐
PUT {{host}}/userplat/recharge/package
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "packageId": {{packageId}},
  "packageName": "测试套餐-已修改",
  "rechargeMoney": 88.00,
  "giftMoney": 12.00,
  "enableState": 1
}

### 删除充值套餐
DELETE {{host}}/userplat/recharge/package?packageId={{packageId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ======== 支付回调接口 ========

### 充值支付成功回调
POST {{host}}/userplat/pay/callback/recharge/success?outTradeNo={{outTradeNo}}&transactionId=transaction_{{outTradeNo}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 模拟支付成功（仅用于测试）
POST {{host}}/userplat/pay/callback/recharge/mock/success?outTradeNo={{outTradeNo}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ======== 常用流程示例 ========

### 1. 获取充值套餐列表
### 2. 创建充值订单（选择套餐进行充值）
### 3. 支付成功回调（通常由支付平台调用，这里用模拟接口）
### 4. 查询钱包余额
### 5. 查询余额流水记录